      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. While it remains a reliable daily driver, it shows its age with several cosmetic imperfections, including some noticeable scratches on the passenger side and minor upholstery wear in the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, though it will likely need a new set of tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance tasks.",
      "price": 20000.0,
