    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market. This specimen arrives in showroom-ready condition, having been maintained to the most exacting mechanical and aesthetic standards. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. For the buyer seeking an investment-grade driving experience, this vehicle offers uncompromising quality and peerless value. Turn-key ready and awaiting its next curator.",
