    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, keeping it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and only bringing it out for those perfect sunny afternoon cruises. It\u2019s in truly spectacular shape\u2014honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh feel. I\u2019m only parting with it to make some space in the driveway, but I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by, have a coffee, and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 43900.0,
