      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute pinnacle of the E46 M3 platform. This S54-powered masterpiece features a fully documented VANOS overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural rigidity of the chassis matches its legendary drivetrain. The 3.2L straight-six retains its factory-spec compression across all cylinders, delivering razor-sharp throttle response through its individual throttle bodies. Every bushing has been inspected for compliance, and the Getrag 6-speed shifts with bolt-action precision. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanically synchronized instrument, dialed in for the discerning enthusiast who understands that 'preventative maintenance' is the highest form of care. Investment-grade and ready for the canyon or the collection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
